data.description: Adorable 3 bedroom 1.5 bath home. Completely cozy with a covered front porch to sit out and sip your tea or coffee in. This house had a new roof installed in 2022 with solar panels helping you save some money on utilities. Also, who doesn’t love hard wood flooring throughout the house?! The kitchen has double ovens and so much cabinet space! Most windows have been updated to vinyl and the back yard is a great size, totally spacious, with a big shed as a plus. This house has been well kept up with, come and check it out and add your finishing touches to it!
